title: Ishule hamro jeevan lai
lyrics:
Ishule hamro jeevan lai
Ishule hamro pap lai dhoi dene chan.
'Aunu hos -2 mukti linu lai -2
(1)
Chini hamro Prabhu Ishu raja lai
Bishwas garo unai ma aajnai -2
'Aunu hos -2 shanti linu lai -2
(2)
Uni hon shanti dine Prabhu
Uni hon bato swarga ko -2
'Aunu hos -2 jeevan linu lai -2
